{"tid":394561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】男子順利邨墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-09-10T05:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T01:35:11.000Z","uid":20933,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36af5bc42c9f1bdb9d33d9dbac7db7fbcb51204b","tid":394561,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1505019320_be88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1505019320_be88.jpg&h=0222e984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上11時許，秀茂坪順利邨利祥樓，一名男子疑由高處墮下，倒卧在利祥樓對開地面，奄奄一息，救護員接報到場，證實男事主當場不治，地上遺下疑為死者的一對鞋，警員經調查後，相信男事主52歲，據悉，有精神病紀錄。"},{"pid":"41b1169e061634fefd2d615e7a24d1690fec4030","tid":394561,"uid":7954,"like":568,"dislike":4,"score":564,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f1e7ef83838d1468af156a64c5458a2ec4f48fd","tid":394561,"uid":22832,"like":261,"dislike":9,"score":252,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:21:18.000Z","msg":"睇錯左男子順利墮樓亡"},{"pid":"d85b71207d574386bca07a544b89bc48291886a1","tid":394561,"uid":20903,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:22:20.000Z","msg":"幾靚喎張相"},{"pid":"b327f44d82e0994db67fdbbb8e709ced010ed886","tid":394561,"uid":51250,"like":73,"dislike":2,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:22:29.000Z","msg":"天井式公屋真係好撚恐怖"},{"pid":"747ee2f6990c60e528bd4637e4c8705f63ed09bb","tid":394561,"uid":7840,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:22:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f986a2e926b7935ea1f06690898e557386c93ff2","tid":394561,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d044ccf594fbbbae5c06a1c03bb29a43063f26","tid":394561,"uid":1386,"like":258,"dislike":2,"score":256,"citedBy":0,"re